QtoSetDef.Name: Qto_ArchElementBaseQuantities
QtoSetDef.Definition: Base quantities that are common to the definition of all occurrences of arch elements.

QtoDef.Name: Length
QtoDef.Definition:
The length of the object.
The axis arch length from the profile center of gravity.

QtoDef.Name: Volume
QtoDef.Definition:
Volume of the element.
Total volume of the arch element.

QtoDef.Name: CrossSectionArea
QtoDef.Definition: The cross section area of the arch element.

QtoDef.Name: OuterSurfaceArea
QtoDef.Definition: The outer surface area of the arch element.

QtoDef.Name: InnerSurfaceArea
QtoDef.Definition: The inner surface area of the arch element.
